text: Saint-Martin Dam is a dam in Mont-Valin, Quebec, Canada, in the administrative region of Saguenay–Lac-Saint-Jean and the regional county municipality of Le Fjord-du-Saguenay. ==Other dams with this name == *Barrage Saint-Martin in 32000 Auch, Gers, France *Barrage Saint-Martin in 89100 Sens, Yonne, France *Saint-Martin Dam near the village of Quartier Militaire in Mauritius. ==References== * Category:Dams in Quebec
title: Saint-Martin Dam
